FYI, from the April DOJ Libraries Newsletter, "Countering QAnon: Understanding the 
Role of Human Trafficking in the Disinformation-Extremist Nexus." 
https://polarisproject.org/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/Polaris-Report-Countering-
QAnon.pdf  Epstein gets mentioned, starting at page nine. 
This also mentions in passing that radicalized people search for QAnon merchandise to 
buy on the internet. Seems to me that if that is so, that is a path to follow to people 
doing this to make money. Not for you all, but perhaps for another Unit. Be well. 
EFTA00030018
